<TEXT>
	   Butler said he would report Thursday to the Security Council.
	   A similar account of the talks' collapse was given by Gustavo
Zlauvinen, Butler's legal adviser, after his arrival in Bahrain.
	   Zlauvinen said Butler had offered Aziz a new work schedule for
