showers or thunderstorms. High 85 to 95. Wind east to northeast at
around 15 mph.
	   Tonight... Becoming variably cloudy with scattered showers and
isolated thunderstorms. Low 75 to 85. Wind northeast 5 to 10 mph.
Chance of rain 40 percent.
