<SLUG> BC-Greece-Fires, 1st Ld-Writethru,0494 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
State of emergency declared in forest fire area near Athens
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Eds: UPDATES with premier cutting short vacation, some fires dying
down, others under control. &QL; 
