<SLUG> BC-APNewsAlert,0023 </SLUG>


<TEXT>
	   Dow closes down 293 points, according to preliminary figures, in
third-biggest point loss ever.
</TEXT>
(PROFILE
(WS SL:BC-APNewsAlert; CT:f; 
(REG:EURO;)
(REG:BRIT;)
(REG:SCAN;)
(REG:MEST;)
